<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear investors,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I hope this mail finds you well.</span><o:p></o=
:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"HE" dir=3D"RTL"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please find attached an Executive Summary of Q1=
 2022 activity.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">In addition, you received an additional mail fr=
om the fund's administrator (Tzur) with a link to the following documents:<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;ms=
o-list:l1 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Financial Statements for Q1-2022<o:p></o:p></span></li=
><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;m=
so-list:l1 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Capital Account as of March 31, 2022<o:p></o:p></span>=
</li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:le=
ft;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Capital Call Notice <o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please let me know if you have any further ques=
tions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
